label: انموذج العلوم لارباب الفهوم / لعلامة عصره وفريد دهره مفتي الثقلين الطرسوسي.
Unmūzaj al-ʻulūm li-arbāb al-fuhūm / li-ʻallāmah ʻaṣrihi wa-farīd dahrihi muftī al-thaqalayn al-Ṭarasūsī.
description: Number of lines per page varies, as does the written surface (see individual records). Written in black ink with use of red, yellow and green. There are three main scripts in the volume: fol. 2b-75b (text 1); fol. 76a-77b, and fol. 78a-169b. European glazed paper. Table of contents on fol. 1b. Ownership statement signed al-Sayyid Aḥmad Rifʻat on fol. 1a. Ownership statements in Turkish dated from the 13th c. H. [19th c.] on fol. 181b. Foliation using Arabic numerals (starting on fol. 2). Modern foliation in pencil using Western numerals (with two fol. 178).

Contains also in the margins, at the end of the main texts, and on small pieces of paper placed between the leaves, excerpts from several other texts, such as al-Kulliyāt by Abū al-Baqāʼ (Kaffawī, Ayyūb ibn Mūsá, d. 1682 or 3), al-Taʻrīfāt by al-Munāwī (d. 1621), Anwār al-tanzīl by ʻAbd Allāh ibn ʻUmar al-Bayḍawī (d. 1286?), Bustān al-ʻĀrifīn by Abū Layth al-Samarqandī (d. 983?), al-Tawḍīḥ by Ṣadr al-sharīʻah (ʻUbayd Allāh al-Maḥbūbī, d. 1346 or 7), al-Talwīḥ by Masʻūd ibn ʻUmar al-Taftāzānī (d. 1389?), the Zīj of Ibn al-Shāṭir (d. 1375), excerpts from untitled texts signed al-Khayālī, al-Ḥaddādī, al-Tūqātī, and from unsigned texts entitled Jāmiʻ ikhtilāf al-madhāhib, Gharāʼib al-Qurʼān, Kitāb Rashaḥāt ʻayn al-ḥayāh, Risālat Ḥall dāʼirat al-muʻaddil, Risālat ʻIlm al-ḥikmah, etc.
Incipit: بسم ... حامدا لله ومصليا ومسلما على نبيه واله ومرضيا على اصحابه ... هذا انموزج من العلوم جمعته لارباب الفهوم انخراطاً فى سلك الاقدمين
Explicit: واستعانوا فيها بالقلم ورسم الجداول فما وصلوا الى استخراج الجذر التحقيقى بل قنعوا هناك بالتقريب تمت

metadata.label: Author
value: Ṭaraṣūṣī, Ibrāhīm ibn ʻAlī, 1320-approximately 1356

metadata.label: Abstract
value: Collection of texts on the classification of sciences and astronomy, with tables and figures.

metadata.label: Contents
value: 1. fol. 2b-75b : al-Unmūzaj al-ʻulūm lil-arbāb al-fuhūm / [Ibrāhīm ibn ʻAlī] al-Ṭarsūsī [al-Ḥanafī] (d. 1356)
2. fol. 76a-81b : al-Sharḥ fī al-dāʼirah al-hindīyah li-mawlānā Ṣadr al-sharīʻah / Ḥusayn al-Ḥusaynī al-Khalkhālī (d. 1605).
3. fol. 82a-83a : [Excerpts from a text by al-Sayyid ʻAlī al-Jaghmūnī and from the Risālat muʻaddil al-nahār by al-Salīmī, with two figures].
4. fol. 83b-88a : Risālah mukhtaṣarah fī asmāʼ al-rusūm al-marsūmah ʻalá al-ālah al-musammāh bi-al-usṭurlāb al-shamālī.
5. fol. 88b-94b : al-Risālah fī al-usṭurlāb / ʻAbd al-Ḥalīm al-Qayṣarī [Söilemzādeh].
6. fol. 95a-99b : Tashrīḥ al-aflāk / Bahāʼ al-Dīn Muḥammad al-ʻĀmilī (d. 1621).
7. fol. 100a-102a : [Short excerpts from several texts, in Arabic and Turkish].
8. fol. 102b-105a : Rūznāmah / Darendeli.
9. fol. 105b-107a : Rūznāmah / Qāḍīʹzādah, Mūsá ibn Muḥammad (d. ca. 1436).
10. fol. 107b : Awwal al-burūj min Risālat al-Rubʻ al-mujayyab [with a figure] / ʻAlī al-Jaghmūnī(?).
11. fol. 108a-131b : Naḍrat al-lubāb fī sharḥ Bahjat al-albāb / Muḥammad ibn ʻAlī al-Ḥumaydī (d. 1765 or 6).
12. fol. 131b-132a : al-Risālah fī rubʻ al-dāʼirah fī jānib al-muqanṭarāt. Bāb 21 / Muḥammad ibn Kātib Sinān (d. 1523?).
13. fol. 132a : [Portion of a text on the lunar mansions] / al-Waḥdatī.
14. fol. 132b-135b : Tuḥfat al-mukhtaṣarāt fī maʻrifat al-qiblah wa-awqāt al-ṣalawāt / Muḥammad Sibṭ al-Māridīnī (b. 1423).
15. fol. 136a-139a : Risālah fī al-ʻamal bi-al-rubʻ al-marsūm ʻalay-hā al-muqanṭarāt / Shihāb al-Dīn Aḥmad ibn al-Majdī (d. 1447).
16. fol. 139a-143a : Risālat al-Kurah / Muḥammad ibn ʻAlī al-Ḥumaydī (d. 1765 or 6).
17. fol. 143b-146a : Ḥāshīyah ʻalá Sharḥ al-Mulakhkhaṣ / ʻAbd al-Karīm al-Niẓāmī (15th cent.).
18. fol. 146b-165b : al-Kitāb fī sharḥ al-Mulakhkhaṣ li-Jighmīnī / Mūsá ibn Muḥammad Qāḍīʹzādah (d. ca. 1436).
19. fol. 166a-169b : [Risālah fī al-ʻamal bi-al-asṭurlāb] / Ḥaydar ibn ʻAbd al-Raḥmān al-Jazarī.
20. fol. 170a-181a : [Blank].
21. fol. 181b : [Inscriptions in Turkish].
22. fol. 182 : [Blank].
